</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="0C0E8B98F677CCA3E2DAA70B8C901F3F" pageId="0" pageNumber="107" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="88B1F16858DF03045BA2CE6501B58EA8" pageId="0" pageNumber="107">Distribution and ecology.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="9E51535633A82E5A2D9B2A05E7AF9CF7" pageId="0" pageNumber="107">
Eurasian, introduced to the north of South America. Predominantly found in grazed 
<normalizedToken id="A7FD0AC74E83200167724DE42AB823B8" originalValue="pÃ¡ramo">paramo</normalizedToken>
and puna vegetation. 
<taxonomicName id="55C78A05530A3F4B25A701921C23EE56" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Agrostis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Agrostis capillaris" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="107" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="capillaris">
<emphasis id="39475DA400CFCAC1A67CB11E5BCDDD01" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="107">Agrostis capillaris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is here recorded as a new regional record for the Depto. 
<normalizedToken id="C0536CCFAAFA6E067B89288AC5D817BD" originalValue="BoyacÃ¡">Boyaca</normalizedToken>
of Colombia. 
<bibRefCitation id="66F18C22A8A4832A6442EC2A56FDF75C" author="Giraldo-Canas, D" editor="Bernal, R" journalOrPublisher="2). Instituto de Ciencias Naturales, Universidad Nacional de Colombia, Bogota D. C." pageId="0" pageNumber="107" pagination="2127 - 2205" refId="B10" refString="Giraldo-Canas, D, Londono, X, Clark, LG, 2016. Poaceae. In: Bernal, R, Gradstein, SR, Celis, M, Eds., Catalogo de plantas y liquenes de Colombia (Vol. 2). Instituto de Ciencias Naturales, Universidad Nacional de Colombia, Bogota D.C.: 2127 - 2205" title="Poaceae." volumeTitle="Catalogo de plantas y liquenes de Colombia (Vol." year="2016">
<normalizedToken id="FF72BC9AD00AA05659EA87F4D8DB4542" originalValue="Giraldo-CaÃ±as">Giraldo-Canas</normalizedToken>
et al. (2016)
</bibRefCitation>
mention it as an introduced and cultivated herb based on the record of 
<taxonomicName id="9A6FFD1ABA450F4FFA9FBD50FCD9E908" genus="A." lsidName="A. tenuis" pageId="0" pageNumber="107" rank="species" species="tenuis">
<emphasis id="AF80D865A84407F77D24793B8DC201AA" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="107">A. tenuis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="518B2745290A92A6FAF2DE07ECEE1BC5" author="Hafliger, E" journalOrPublisher="2). Instituto de Ciencias Naturales, Universidad Nacional de Colombia, Bogota D. C." pageId="0" pageNumber="107" refId="B11" refString="Hafliger, E, Scholz, H, 1981. Grass weeds 2. Weeds of the subfamilies Chloridoideae, Pooideae, Oryzoideae. Ciba-Geigy Ltd., Basil." title="Grass weeds 2. Weeds of the subfamilies Chloridoideae, Pooideae, Oryzoideae. Ciba-Geigy Ltd., Basil." year="1981">Hafliger and Scholz (1981)</bibRefCitation>
. It is likely to be an under-recorded element in many Colombian regions with 
<normalizedToken id="DE220ED9776D5B239D9B8D57EA85042D" originalValue="pÃ¡ramo">paramo</normalizedToken>
habitat.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
